<HEAD>Search Resumes For Helicopter, Iran Attacks Two Neutral Ships</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: SUBS 4 grafs for grafs 21-22 pvs ``In a report...'' to update
with Pentagon comment. New 15th graf ``However, the Pentagon...''
with Pentagon denying that convoys halted. DELETES 3rd graf pvs as
