RGANIZATION>, he said. It hopes to set up a system that will allow small orders of stock entered though the one exchange to be executed in the other, he said. `` Today we have the technical and now the legal ability to create what amounts to a trans-Atlantic stock market,'' <PERSON> Hardiman </PERSON> said.
