C </ORGANIZATION>,'' said <PERSON> Bruce </PERSON> <PERSON> Watts </PERSON> of <ORGANIZATION> Needham </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> & </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> amp </ORGANIZATION><ORGANIZATION> ; </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Co. </ORGANIZATION> `` It's partly intended to place them in a strongly competitive position when <ORGANIZATION> IBM </ORGANIZATION> announces its code-named Silverlake products this summer.'' `` DEC is getting their products out into the market first in order to prevent <ORGANIZATION> IBM </ORGANIZATION> from taking customers away,'' he said. The company said the single-processor 6210 computer provides 2.8 times the performance of its VAX 11 @ 780 system. The system can accommodate up to four processors at once. Upgrades will cost betweem $ 100,200 and $ 173,500, <ORGANIZATION> Digital </ORGANIZATION> said. <ORGANIZATION> Digital </ORGANIZATION>'s earnings in its third fiscal quarter ending March 26 totaled $ 305.1 million, or $ 2.33 a share, down from $ 307.6 million, or $ 2.29 a share, one year earlier. The company had reduced its earnings estimates for the quarter because of sluggish sales of expensive computer systems and a shift in demand to smaller lines. Digital on Tuesday also announced a new version of its <ORGANIZATION> VMS </ORGANIZATION> software and a new FORTRAN version for symmetric multiprocessing. Meanwhile, <ORGANIZATION> IBM </ORGANIZATION> on Tuesday announced upgraded software to take advantage of design changes in its mainframe computers.
